to record it one day. It--

590
00:27:50,481 --> 00:27:53,651
He… He's a piece of shit, Mom.

591
00:27:53,734 --> 00:27:55,820
It's not about you. It's him.

592
00:27:55,903 --> 00:27:58,531
It-- it's not about you picking
